# Public canonical site URL (used for canonical, hreflang, OG tags, sitemap).
# - Leave unset on Vercel previews → falls back to VERCEL_URL automatically.
# - Set in Vercel "Production" environment to the real domain once wired
#   (e.g. https://toaster.studio).
# - Set locally in .env.local if you want canonical URLs to use a real host
#   instead of http://localhost:3000.
NEXT_PUBLIC_SITE_URL=

# Supabase (added when migrations land — placeholders for now)
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL=
# NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=
# SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=
